fields.name: Ilaun
fields.description:
A fresh light perfume. The top notes of the wild Fragrant Orchid capture the scents of a summer's day and blends with the woody base notes of ferns, lichens and mosses.
Blended and bottled by hand at the Burren Perfumery.

fields.name: Frond
fields.description:
A sophisticated, feminine perfume possessing warmth, sensuality and an underlying complexity. The freshness of cut grasses sharpens the rich scents of Wild Rose, Violet and Ylang Ylang with the soft Sandalwood base notes bringing depth and finish.
Blended and bottled by hand at the Burren Perfumery.

fields.name: Summer Harvest
fields.description: Summer Harvest recalls lying in a meadow on summer's afternoon. A delicate, floral fragrance with notes of Meadowsweet, Lady's Bedstraw and a hint of Chamomile.

fields.name: Aran
fields.description: A fragrance for men and women. A modern fresh sea cologne with a citrus top note and woody base notes of the mosses, lichens and barks of the Burren.

fields.name: Winter Woods
fields.description:
Winter Woods opens with the freshness of Rosemary, Bergamot and Lemon, leads into subtle notes of Iris and Lavender and develops as a woody blend of Cedar, Pine and Vetiver for a long-lasting, quietly masculine fragrance.
Blended and bottled by hand at the Burren Perfumery.

fields.name: Autumn Harvest
fields.description: We blended Autumn Harvest to evoke the scents encountered on a walk in the Autumn woods. The deep woody notes of Blackberry leaves and Blackcurrant are mixed with the scent of Nettles and Wild Marjoram.

fields.name: White Christmas
fields.description: ‘White Christmas’ brings a warm seasonal scent featuring spicy top notes of incense, orange and bergamot, heart notes of cinnamon, cloves and patchouli on a base of amber, sandalwood and vanilla all brought together to create a welcoming winter aroma in your home.

fields.name: True Lavender
fields.description: Our blend of lavender oils from the south of France create a classic relaxing fragrance to help you unwind and restore harmony.

fields.name: White Pomegranate
fields.description: Fresh pomegranate infused with exotic rosebuds reveal a heart of lily and gardenia. Cassis and vanilla add warmth to this relaxing and romantic fragrance.

fields.name: Pink Pepper
fields.description: A rich glamourous fragrance, Pink Pepper has become a classic since first introduced as part of the Coffee Collection 2015. Top notes of Pink pepper, neroli and pear lead to a heart of jasmine and coffee with rich base notes of vanilla, patchouli and cedarwood.

fields.name: Lemongrass and Ginger
fields.description: Subtle citrus herbs and mild woody spiced ginger. From your kitchen to your bathroom, enjoy this cleansing and uplifting aroma.

fields.name: Italian Apothecary
fields.description: Exploring the ancient streets of Florence inspired us to create this fragrance. Comforting spicy top notes with a musky heart of patchouli and clove leading to a woody base of amber and sandalwood.

fields.name: Acqua Viva
fields.description: This fresh and energizing fragrance has top notes of mandarin, orange, lemon and cassis lead to a heart of cardamom and pepper with underlying base notes of musk, amber and cedarwood.

fields.name: Dodici
fields.description: Sicilian lemon and marjoram on a backdrop of Tuscan lavender. This unique perfume with oils of rosemary will invigorate.
